Module it.polimi.ingsw.PSP034

Package it.polimi.ingsw.PSP034.messages.gameOverPhase

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EndByDisconnection
    Message sent by the server to the client that communicates another player's disconnection.
    GameOverAnswer
    Answer from the client to the server, in response to a RequestGameOver.
    GameOverRequest
    Request from the server to the client, during the end phase of a player's game.
    PersonalDefeatRequest
    Message sent from the server to the client that communicates to a player tha he/she lost the game and who is the winner, if there is one.
    SingleLoserInfo
    Message from the server to the client that communicates to a player that another player lost the game (but there is no winner yet).
    WinnerRequest
    Message from the server to the client that communicates to a player that he/she won.
